---

<section class="bg-bg-soft">
  <div class="container-tight pb-20">
    <div
      class="fade-in relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-line bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500 to-cyan-500 p-8 md:p-12 text-white shadow-lift"
    >
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20 pointer-events-none"
        style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 85% 25%, rgba(255,255,255,0.5), transparent 45%);"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>

      <div class="relative grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] md:items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/80">
            NSF GRFP — Happy to Help
          </p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tightish leading-snug max-w-2xl">
            The NSF Graduate Research Fellowship has been transformative for my career.
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base md:text-lg text-white/90 max-w-2xl">
            I'm happy to discuss the application process and share my research and personal statements with prospective applicants. Don't hesitate to reach out.
          </p>
        </div>

        <a
          href="mailto:sur4002@med.cornell.edu"
          class="inline-flex h-fit items-center gap-2 self-start md:self-center rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-ink-900 hover:bg-white/90 transition-colors shadow-lg"
        >
          Get in touch
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
